                        <interp inst="t18370403-name-1186" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN WOODGET</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a police-constable. Mary Lucas described the prisoner to me—he was standing on the opposite side to Lucas's shop in Lawrence-street, which leads into the Rookery—I secured him.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I never was in the shop in my life.</p>
